According to the image on the screen, we can see a blank document and an Insert button. To select the Insert button in the editor, we need to do the following:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 169, "height": 40}}
]
```This selects the Insert button and clicks it.
